{"tid":1405403,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"藍大仙都變返黃大仙，將軍澳可唔可以將一次軍","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:02:37.000Z","uid":104225,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2bf24cc00bd0fac4f32f7ee90e6dcb67ade36cb","tid":1405403,"uid":104225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"成日話「將軍澳得兩條路一封就冇得走」<br />\n調返轉諗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反而可以係出面既狗入唔到嚟增援</span></span><br />\n同埋除咗翠林同隧道之外<br />\n仲有條路可以由西貢去到馬鞍山<br />\n再唔係仲有得行山  退場根本唔成問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新界九龍服既咪去西環啦</span></span><br />\n西區地圖大家打慣打熟  最熟手嗰啲大師一定出曬去<br />\n新手想升LV 將軍澳絕對係不二之選<br />\n街坊就更加唔洗講！<br />\n相信落開場既大家都知街坊有幾重要<br />\n<br />\n利申  呢兩個月第一次開POST<br />\n意圖、背景、身份相當明顯<br />\n但我絕對有資格講呢啲野"},{"pid":"88ac3e7f122802efc3a8ad8ee7c65dc8140da8b6","tid":1405403,"uid":104225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"景林隔音屏要人"},{"pid":"b0dc45a9d8d342645bcb754e0dd9c7f43ed0c225","tid":1405403,"uid":104225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da6abdbb3b4336ddcc61d34880cc953079c64997","tid":1405403,"uid":104225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d01d0566e99ebb9e4c458bedfbb465c356d498a","tid":1405403,"uid":60299,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b39fe38d05892ee5ba4966a12dc2492be926329","tid":1405403,"uid":104225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"2300隔音屏已快閃"}]}